text: "Daddy" is a song by English singer and songwriter Tulisa, released as a single on 5 April 2019 by Xploded/Universal Music. Tulisa co-wrote the track with David Lucius King. Tulisa's first release in three years, it was called her comeback single, and was reportedly the first in a "quickfire" set of songs she will release. ==Critical reception== NME called the track "playful" and "dancehall-flecked", as well as a return to Tulisa's "urban roots". ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:Tulisa songs Category:Hip hop soul songs Category:Dancehall songs Category:R&B; songs
title: Daddy (Tulisa song)
